name: Spanish Tapas
description: Authentic tapas including Manchego cheese, imported Spanish Serrano ham, chorizo sausage, almond-stuffed olives, grilled eggplant and stuffed cherry peppers.

name: Mini Empanadas
description: Savoury little empanadas served with a kicky chipotle dip. Flavours include chicken, beef, and spinach with feta. One flavour per tray.

name: Chicken Tenders
description: The perfect addition to your party buffet. Chicken tenders with plum sauce.

name: Risotto Cakes
description: A dreamy little side dish. Creamy risotto cakes served with Longo’s Artichoke Asiago dip.

name: Chicken Caesar Salad
description: The all-time favourite with a bit of protein. Lettuce, croutons, real bacon bits, Parmesan cheese, white chicken meat.

name: Coleslaw Salad
description: A cool and creamy addition. Fresh cabbage and carrots in a vinaigrette dressing.

name: Caesar Salad
description: A refreshing combination of crisp ingredients. Lettuce, croutons, real bacon bits, Parmesan cheese.

name: Pesto Tortellini
description: Delicious tortellini stuffed with ricotta, Parmesan and Romano cheese tossed in a light pesto dressing.

name: Taste of Italy
description: Stunningly arranged Italian antipasti. Capicollo, cacciatore sausage, dry-cured prosciutto, soppressata salami, mini cocktail bocconcini, mortadella, asiago, Sicilian olives.

name: Slim & Tasty Wraps
description: Wraps cut into quarters including portions of tuna salad, egg salad and grilled vegetables. Served with roasted red pepper dip.

name: Sandwich Combo
description: A classic combination of sandwiches and wraps. Includes egg salad, tuna salad, Black Forest ham, roast chicken and roast beef.

name: Veal Cutlets
description: Classic scaloppine with a Longo’s touch. Breaded veal cutlets.

name: Meat Shells
description: Meaty morsels on a bed of fresh tomato sauce. Fresh pasta, ground beef, marinara sauce and Parmesan cheese.

name: Mini Square Dessert Tray
description: A gorgeous arrangement of assorted square-shaped desserts made with real cream.

name: Sweet Creations Tray
description: Finish things off with these decadent mini pastries, made with velvety cream.

name: Sliced Fruit Tray
description: A light and refreshing dessert addition. Cantaloupe, honeydew, pineapple and strawberries.

name: Veggie Tray
description: Super fresh, crisp vegetables. Baby carrots, celery, cauliflower, broccoli, peppers, cucumbers and cherry tomatoes, with Longo’s Ranch dip.

name: Soft Cheese Selection
description: A unique assortment of domestic and imported French cheeses including Douanier, Bleu d’Auvergne, Château Bourgogne and Sauvagine.

name: Greek Pasta Salad
description: A heartier take on the Mediterranean classic. Penne pasta, green and red peppers, black olives, feta cheese, olives, dressing.

name: Red Potato & Herb Salad
description: Luscious red potatoes with a fragrant finish. Red potatoes, onions, parsley, dill, vinegar, spices.

name: Cheese Taster
description: The perfect snack for cheese lsovers. Bite-sized pieces of Canadian Emmenthal, Muenster, flavoured havarti, smoked mozzarella, Canadian medium cheddar and marble. Arranged with grapes and strawberries.

name: Shrimp Feast
description: A fresh favourite for any occasion. Jumbo shrimp, cocktail sauce, lemon wedges.

name: Sandwich Bites
description: An exciting variety of finger-sized, sliced bread sandwiches. Selection includes Black Forest ham, roast beef, turkey, chicken, egg salad and tuna salad. Served with dill pickles cherry tomatoes and baby carrots.

name: New York Style Deli
description: A taste of Manhattan. Includes roast beef and cheddar on pumpernickel, pastrami and swiss on rye, and spiced turkey and cheddar Emmenthal on sourdough. Served with dill pickles, cherry tomatoes and dijonnaise.

name: Mini Croissants
description: Buttery little croissants perfect for brunch. Includes turkey, ham, roast beef, tuna salad and egg salad.

name: Grilled Chicken Breast
description: A flavourful and healthy basic for any party. Grilled chicken breast.

name: Cannelloni
description: A mouth-watering main dish. Fresh pasta, ground veal, marinara sauce, mozzarella and Parmesan cheese.

name: Manicotti
description: The ultimate combination of ricotta and spinach. Fresh pasta, ricotta cheese, spinach, marinara sauce, mozzarella and Parmesan cheese.

name: Eggplant Rollatini
description: An authentic Italian classic that every family will love. Sliced eggplant, ricotta cheese, marinara sauce and Parmesan cheese.

name: Decadent Delight Squares
description: Delightful little bites of some of ourdecadent treats. Killer Brownies® and mini squares

name: Breaded Perogies
description: Little pockets of heaven. Breaded potato perogies with Longo’s Parmesan Cheese & Red Pepper dip.

name: Garden Salad
description: A rainbow-bright display of fresh garden produce. Lettuce, cherry tomatoes, cucumbers, carrots, peppers.

name: Greek Salad
description: Flavours of the Mediterranean. Lettuce, peppers, cucumbers, Kalamata olives, red onions, cherry tomatoes, feta cheese.

name: California Salad
description: A fruity ray of California sunshine. Mixed greens, mandarin slices, strawberries, slivered almonds.

name: Fancy Bean Salad
description: Crisp and colourful. Kidney, black turtle and navy beans; black eyed peas; chick peas; red, green and yellow peppers; sweet onions; fresh parsley; olive oil.

name: Italian Charcuterie
description: A selection of the finest traditional Italian cold cuts. Fellino salami, pancetta, imported Parma prosciutto, Culatello, Auricchio, oven-dried olives, dried figs and Rosemary flatbreads.

name: All Natural Deli
description: An appetizing arrangement of naturally made deli meats. McLean’s Tuscan turkey and roast beef, and oven roast chicken and ham. Served alongside Swiss Emmenthal cheese and dijonnaise.

name: Vegetarian Deli
description: A tasty, meat-free selection, including cucumber and cream cheese, egg salad, cheese, and grilled vegetables.

name: Steamed Vegetable Medley
description: A healthy assortment of steamed veggies including asparagus, broccoli, cauliflower, zucchini, red and yellow peppers, mini carrots, and red onion.

name: Smoked Chicken Ravioli
description: A Longo’s favourite. Fresh ravioli stuffed with perfectly smoked chicken and cheese. Dressed in a vodka sauce and Parmesan cheese.

name: Longo’s Signature Frutta di Bosco
description: An Italian masterpiece of cream and berries. Golden buttery crust, filled with rich pastry cream and topped with blackberries, raspberries and blueberries.

name: Firm Cheese Favourites
description: Firm favourites from around the globe featuring Merlot BellaVitano, Beemster XO, Auricchio & Manchego.

name: BBQ Wings
description: Smokey and delicious BBQ flavoured chicken wings served with creamy Longo’s Ranch dip.

name: Macaroni Salad
description: Large elbow macaroni in a unique dressing mixed with diced celery, shredded carrots, Spanish onion and red peppers.

name: Cranberry Quinoa & Pumpkin Seeds Salad
description: A twist in the right direction, Quinoa, dried cranberries, raisins and toasted pumpkin seeds all married together and dressed in a delicious honey and white wine vinegar dressing.

name: Cilantro Tabouleh Salad
description: A refreshing mix of bulgur, tomatoes, cucumber and quinoa combined with a light dressing of fresh herbs.

name: Potato & Egg Salad
description: Potato and diced egg in a unique dressing mixed with diced celery, shredded carrots, onion and red peppers.

name: Connoisseur’s Choice
description: Fine shavings of Longo’s Signature deli meats. Roast beef, Black Forest ham, oven roast turkey, Montreal smoked beef, and shaved Swiss cheese, served with dijonnaise.

name: Fruit and Cheese
description: A world tour of cheeses. Longo’s double cream brie, Original Swiss Emmenthal, Canadian Oka, Longo’s original goat cheese, extra old cheddar and blue cheese. Served with a fig spread and an assortment of fresh fruit.

name: Focaccia Fingers
description: Fresh, finger-sized sandwiches on focaccia bread. Includes deli meats, cheese and grilled vegetables. Served with Asiago artichoke dip.

name: Grilled Salmon
description: An elegant addition to any menu. Grilled salmon.

name: Vegetable Rice
description: The ideal side dish. Fluffy rice with celery, carrots, onions, broccoli, mushrooms, peas and spices.

name: Black Grain Firecracker
description: An aromatic and gorgeous coming together of superfoods, black rice, black barley, black quinoa, combined with carrot and yellow pepper tossed in a light dressing.

name: Cheese Shells
description: A stunning celebration of soft Italian cheese. Fresh pasta shells, ricotta cheese, marinara sauce and mozzarella cheese.

name: Tomato & Asiago Ravioli
description: A pairing that is full of flavour. Fresh pasta, hand-stuffed with ricotta, asiago and grilled tomatoes. Dressed in a rosé sauce and Parmesan cheese.

name: Morning Glory
description: A sweet way to start the day. Mini croissants, mini danishes, pound cake and crunchies.

name: Breakfast or Brunch
description: Freshly baked treats worth waking up for. Bagels, muffins and croissants.

name: European Cookie Tray
description: Specialty biscuits from across the pond. Assorted European cookies.

name: Fruit Cocktail Bowl
description: A fresh medley of juicy favourites. Cantaloupe, honeydew, pineapple, strawberries and grapes.

name: Mini Rice Balls
description: A Sicilian specialty in cocktail-sized bites. Mini rice balls served with Longo’s Tuscan Gorgonzola Red Pepper dip.

name: Samosas
description: A taste of India. Flavourful vegetable samosas with Longo’s Mango Chutney dip.

name: Spring Rolls
description: A party favourite for everyone. Vegetable spring rolls with plum sauce.

name: Wheatberry Salad
description: A sweet and tangy side. Wheatberries, sunflower seeds, red peppers, parsley and raisins in a honey-ginger dressing.

name: Curried Couscous Salad
description: A delicious spin on traditional couscous. With chickpea, raisins and green onion in a lemon and honey dressing.

name: Sandwich Stacker
description: Build the perfect sandwich from top-quality ingredients. Sliced cheddar cheese, Canadian Swiss cheese, roast beef, Black Forest ham, summer sausage, smoked turkey, roasted red pepper spread.

name: Artisan Baguette Sandwiches
description: A delicious assortment of Longo’s gourmet artisan sandwiches, including sweet Black Forest and brie, artichoke and asiago beef, chili lime chicken and zesty Italian and Mediterranean turkey.

name: Pinwheel Wraps
description: Perfect little bites. Includes oven roasted turkey, roast beef and Black Forest ham. Each has cream cheese, lettuce, tomatoes and cheddar cheese. Served with baba ghanouj dip

name: Slider & Pita Combo
description: An inviting display of mini soft slider buns filled with egg, tuna and crab, along with mini pitas filled with assorted meats and cheeses.

name: Classic Sandwich Tray
description: A selection of favourite classic sandwiches on kaiser, cheddar, onion and egg buns. Includes turkey, ham, Montreal smoked meat and roast beef.

name: Chicken Cutlets
description: The perfect comfort food. Tender, breaded chicken cutlets.

name: Roasted Potatoes
description: An irresistible side, prepared to perfection. Roasted potatoes in oil and spices.

name: Beef Lasagna
description: An authentic recipe handed down from generations. Lasagna sheets, ground beef, marinara sauce and mozzarella cheese.

name: Two Bite Tray
description: Satisfyingly sweet and totally permissible. Mini cupcakes, mini tartes, brownies and coconut macaroons.

name: Cookies Galore
description: Make everyone happy with this assortment of Longo’s homemade cookies.

name: Longo’s Signature Dessert Tray
description: Everyone has a favourite here. Includes perfect little cannolis, Killer Brownies® and chocolate dipped strawberries.

name: Killer Brownie® Tray
description: A selection of our decadent and exclusive Killer Brownie® squares.

name: Fruit Tray
description: A colourful platter to please any taste. Cantaloupe, honeydew, pineapple, strawberries, grapes, watermelon, oranges and kiwi.
